lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;2.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Add comments for RTL design, including design features, key signals, logical and sequential behaviors, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;3. Output the comment information in json format.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
