        <mxCell id="N1YDJT1VqBlF1rUJiPrF-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 102, 51); line-height: 140%;&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;[Security Specification Formulation Prompt]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Given the source design file and the corresponded comments as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;[Design Files &amp;amp; Comments]&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Given the threat model corresponded to the design:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;[Threat Model Information]&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;You are required to complete the following tasks:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1. B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;ased on the provided threat model and the RTL design, write the security specification that match the threat model.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;2. Output the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;security specification&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in json format.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The specification description you can refer to the following example:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;at every positive edge of clock, the value of the data register is same as its value in the previous clock cycle if the value of the lock signal in the previous clock cycle i&lt;font&gt;s 1&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="540.36" x="100.36" y="750" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
