        <mxCell id="N1YDJT1VqBlF1rUJiPrF-11" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 102, 51); line-height: 140%;&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;[Assertion Generation Prompt]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Given the source design file and the corresponded comments as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;[Design Files &amp;amp; Comments]&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Given the security specification corresponded to the design:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 128, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;[Security Specification Information]&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;You are required to complete the following tasks:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;1. B&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;ased on the provided&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 128, 0); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;security specification&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and the RTL design,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;translating the information in the specification into security assertions&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 140%;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;2. Output the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;security assertions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in json format.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The specification description you can refer to the following example:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;assert property (@(posedge clk) disable iff (rst) ...)&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
